00:30:00,593 --> 00:30:02,093
You installed a surveillance in the house?

538
00:30:04,080 --> 00:30:05,656
You spied on me?

539
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:10,287
I have no interest in your privacy.

540
00:30:10,328 --> 00:30:12,639
I installed surveillance to
keep an eye on my house,

541
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,542
to protect you.

542
00:30:13,583 --> 00:30:14,843
This isn't spying.

543
00:30:18,770 --> 00:30:21,700
And it just happened to record
what you friend did.

544
00:30:24,762 --> 00:30:26,061
She did it for a reason.

545
00:30:26,102 --> 00:30:29,793
The pills she switched aren't harmful
to the body of the person taking them.

546
00:30:30,084 --> 00:30:31,191
No matter her reason,

547
00:30:31,232 --> 00:30:32,457
no matter what her purpose is,

548
00:30:32,498 --> 00:30:34,226
I found that my pills had been switched,

549
00:30:34,267 --> 00:30:35,746
so I took it for a test.

550
00:30:35,787 --> 00:30:36,840
Nothing wrong with that, right?

551
00:30:39,198 --> 00:30:40,160
No.

552
00:30:43,132 --> 00:30:44,120
Why are you still leaving then?

553
00:30:44,470 --> 00:30:45,480
Get out of the way!

554
00:30:48,463 --> 00:30:49,560
Let go!

555
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,560
Let go!

556
00:30:54,656 --> 00:30:55,536
Stop it, Xia Chu.

557
00:30:55,713 --> 00:30:57,720
Let go! I'm not mad at you!

558
00:30:58,115 --> 00:30:59,066
Who are you mad at then?

559
00:30:59,107 --> 00:31:00,112
I don't want to say.

560
00:31:00,153 --> 00:31:01,113
Then you are mad at me.

561
00:31:01,279 --> 00:31:03,360
No, I'm not mad at you, really!

562
00:31:04,055 --> 00:31:05,320
I just had too much going on today.

563
00:31:05,930 --> 00:31:07,889
First, I found that you took
the drug I gave you for testing,

564
00:31:07,930 --> 00:31:09,206
and I was furious.

565
00:31:09,247 --> 00:31:11,758
I went to see Mi Gu.
I just wanted to complain to her,

566
00:31:11,799 --> 00:31:13,040
I didn't expect that she would tell me...

567
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,016
Forget it, that's not important.

568
00:31:15,618 --> 00:31:17,080
Everything just came together.

569
00:31:17,121 --> 00:31:18,301
I'm in over my head.

570
00:31:18,342 --> 00:31:20,120
I don't know how to digest it.

571
00:31:20,723 --> 00:31:21,663
I need time.

572
00:31:21,704 --> 00:31:23,011
I need space to calm myself down.

573
00:31:23,052 --> 00:31:24,230
I need to get my mind straight.

574
00:31:24,271 --> 00:31:26,320
At least right now, I don't
want to see you, Liang Mu Ze.

575
00:31:27,661 --> 00:31:28,560
No.

576
00:31:33,204 --> 00:31:34,240
Get out of my way!

577
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,964
If you don't want to see me, it's fine.

578
00:31:58,005 --> 00:32:00,149
I can leave, but you can't.

579
00:32:00,190 --> 00:32:01,200
Not to mention that it's night now.

580
00:32:04,496 --> 00:32:05,472
What do you care?

581
00:32:06,143 --> 00:32:07,080
I don't.

582
00:32:07,958 --> 00:32:09,098
I need you.

583
00:32:15,177 --> 00:32:17,427
My cousin is returning
home at the end of the month.

584
00:32:17,631 --> 00:32:18,600
That's your business.

585
00:32:19,560 --> 00:32:21,252
I've sent you her flight number.

586
00:32:21,293 --> 00:32:22,160
Pick her up for me.

587
00:32:22,201 --> 00:32:23,053
Why should I?

588
00:32:23,094 --> 00:32:24,043
She will stay here too.

589
00:32:24,084 --> 00:32:26,400
You two try to bond and
get along with each other.

590
00:32:26,934 --> 00:32:27,937
She will be living here,

591
00:32:27,978 --> 00:32:28,839
but I won't.

592
00:32:30,280 --> 00:32:31,320
Help me out, Xia Chu.

593
00:32:34,159 --> 00:32:35,080
Please?

594
00:32:35,343 --> 00:32:36,191
I really have to leave now.

595
00:32:36,232 --> 00:32:37,102
Call me if you need anything,

596
00:32:37,143 --> 00:32:38,440
but I might not be able to answer it.

597
00:32:39,664 --> 00:32:41,160
I haven't agreed to it yet!

598
00:32:41,889 --> 00:32:43,195
There is another thing I need to tell you.

599
00:32:43,402 --> 00:32:44,320
I don't want to hear it.

600
00:32:49,224 --> 00:32:50,600
Fine, tell me, hurry up.

601
00:32:50,984 --> 00:32:52,262
My cousin,

602
00:32:52,303 --> 00:32:53,280
Liang Shao Xue,

603
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:56,016
she has adult ADHD.

604
00:32:57,748 --> 00:33:00,332
She has difficulty in concentrating
and controlling her emotions.

605
00:33:00,373 --> 00:33:02,875
She also has intermittent depression.

606
00:33:02,965 --> 00:33:05,480
-She can pass out at any time.
-What?

607
00:33:05,946 --> 00:33:06,848
So when you pick her up,

608
00:33:06,889 --> 00:33:08,173
make sure you pay
attention to her condition.

609
00:33:08,214 --> 00:33:10,400
Be careful and more careful, okay?

610
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:11,883
You know she is sick...

611
00:33:11,924 --> 00:33:13,271
and you are still asking
me to pick her up?

612
00:33:13,312 --> 00:33:14,163
Well, you are a doctor.

613
00:33:14,204 --> 00:33:15,604
I am a cardiothoracic surgeon!

614
00:33:15,645 --> 00:33:17,345
That's still a doctor.

615
00:33:17,549 --> 00:33:19,000
Besides, other than you,

616
00:33:19,855 --> 00:33:21,670
I don't trust other people.

617
00:33:22,313 --> 00:33:23,719
So it can only be you, Xia Chu.

618
00:33:26,119 --> 00:33:27,240
Stop flattering me.

619
00:33:28,282 --> 00:33:29,160
All right now.

620
00:33:29,823 --> 00:33:31,880
Be a good girl, Da Miao.
I'll get you some candy when I get back.

621
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,603
Xia Chu,

622
00:33:50,644 --> 00:33:52,760
I bought you some custard
buns and put them in the fridge.

623
00:33:53,300 --> 00:33:54,720
No one's going to
fight you for it this time.

624
00:33:54,761 --> 00:33:55,691
Don't eat too much.

625
00:34:03,214 --> 00:34:04,200
You fool.

626
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:05,997
You bought so many.

627
00:34:06,038 --> 00:34:07,480
How am I going to finish it by myself?

628
00:34:12,862 --> 00:34:14,280
I want to eat some too.

629
00:34:15,198 --> 00:34:16,480
Share it with me.

630
00:35:14,573 --> 00:35:16,073
(Military and police join forces
to dismantle drug dealer den)

631
00:35:34,590 --> 00:35:36,570
(Password: 920218, Dad)

632
00:35:36,883 --> 00:35:39,613
(Pei Yong Yan)

633
00:35:43,613 --> 00:35:44,640
Xiao Ran,

634
00:35:45,395 --> 00:35:46,535
what are you doing?

635
00:35:46,707 --> 00:35:49,520
I'm sorting out the greeting cards
from my friends.

636
00:35:50,541 --> 00:35:51,811
Clean it up and sleep early.

637
00:35:51,852 --> 00:35:52,760
Okay, Mom.

638
00:35:54,979 --> 00:35:55,920
Who is it?

639
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:57,760
Coming.

640
00:36:00,709 --> 00:36:02,084
-Who are you?
-Who are you looking for?

641
00:36:02,125 --> 00:36:04,025
-Who are you looking for?
-What are you doing?

642
00:36:05,015 --> 00:36:05,894
Xiao Ran.

643
00:36:07,896 --> 00:36:10,120
What are you doing?

644
00:36:13,668 --> 00:36:15,328
You're Pei Yong Yan's wife?

645
00:36:15,696 --> 00:36:16,714
Ex-wife.

646
00:36:16,755 --> 00:36:20,040
Did you receive anything
from him recently?

647
00:36:20,559 --> 00:36:21,914
We have been out
of touch for a long time.

648
00:36:23,391 --> 00:36:25,479
I came here to avoid him.

649
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:27,507
I really don't know what
he's doing out there!

650
00:36:27,548 --> 00:36:28,674
Please let us go!

651
00:36:28,715 --> 00:36:30,440
We know nothing!

652
00:36:37,080 --> 00:36:37,960
Where is he?

653
00:36:38,317 --> 00:36:39,240
He's dead.

654
00:36:40,185 --> 00:36:41,560
Even his body is gone.

655
00:36:43,120 --> 00:36:44,280
I'll ask you again.

656
00:36:45,833 --> 00:36:48,560
Did you receive anything
from him recently?

657
00:36:51,350 --> 00:36:52,216
No.

658
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,400
No.

659
00:36:56,214 --> 00:36:57,080
Kill them.

660
00:36:58,968 --> 00:37:00,981
He's dead! I know nothing!

661
00:37:01,022 --> 00:37:02,202
Stop it!

662
00:37:02,243 --> 00:37:03,760
Don't hurt my mom!

663
00:37:03,801 --> 00:37:07,061
I have got the stuff. I'll give it to you.

664
00:37:19,523 --> 00:37:20,603
Is this all?

665
00:37:20,644 --> 00:37:21,640
Yes.

666
00:37:43,733 --> 00:37:44,663
Sir,

667
00:37:44,704 --> 00:37:46,320
please take us in.

668
00:37:52,724 --> 00:37:53,960
I don't want to stay here.

669
00:37:54,381 --> 00:37:56,240
I don't want to live in
the shadow of his crimes.

670
00:37:57,012 --> 00:37:58,604
I want a new life.

671
00:37:58,645 --> 00:38:00,748
Please let us live.

672
00:38:00,789 --> 00:38:03,139
I will do as you say and work for you.

673
00:38:03,180 --> 00:38:05,280
I will do whatever you tell me to do.

674
00:38:05,321 --> 00:38:07,284
-Please.
-Son!

675
00:38:07,325 --> 00:38:08,240
Long Yi.

676
00:38:18,844 --> 00:38:19,920
Please.

677
00:38:29,823 --> 00:38:30,920
You deserve to die.

678
00:38:45,163 --> 00:38:46,840
Nice shot.

679
00:38:51,447 --> 00:38:53,920
Looks like you really hate him.

680
00:38:55,449 --> 00:38:56,885
Even his head is blown off.

681
00:38:58,971 --> 00:38:59,983
I found Gui.

682
00:39:01,644 --> 00:39:02,600
Where is he?

683
00:39:08,844 --> 00:39:10,918
The ID of Zhou Lan,
which we have been monitoring,

684
00:39:10,959 --> 00:39:14,314
was found to have been logged in
by someone else at Xiong's company.

685
00:39:14,355 --> 00:39:18,867
After that, he engaged with someone
with the ID, Buddha on City of Desire.

686
00:39:18,908 --> 00:39:20,914
They agreed to pick up the goods
at Wenhui Hotel...

687
00:39:20,955 --> 00:39:22,535
at 3:00 PM the day after tomorrow.

688
00:39:22,700 --> 00:39:24,160
As for the identity of the other party,

689
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:26,200
it is not yet clear.

690
00:39:30,620 --> 00:39:32,483
Keep an eye on this Xiong person.

691
00:39:32,524 --> 00:39:33,440
Yes, Sir!

692
00:39:33,835 --> 00:39:34,960
So this is Gui?

693
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:37,488
As the founder of the platform,

694
00:39:37,529 --> 00:39:40,880
I have a way of finding out every ID
that appears on the platform.

695
00:39:47,365 --> 00:39:48,280
By the way,

696
00:39:49,122 --> 00:39:53,316
a medical forum will be held
at Wenhui Hotel two days later.

697
00:39:54,581 --> 00:39:57,561
The security measures will definitely
be much tighter than usual.

698
00:39:58,360 --> 00:40:00,468
Yet he chose to hand
out the goods at that place.

699
00:40:00,509 --> 00:40:01,600
Why would he want to do that?

700
00:40:11,868 --> 00:40:12,840
Xia Guang Yuan?

701
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:16,314
Since Gui wants to
replace Old Master so badly,

702
00:40:16,355 --> 00:40:18,255
he won't let go of this opportunity.

703
00:40:18,367 --> 00:40:21,088
Are you saying that Xia Guang Yuan
is his real target?

704
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:26,280
Gui is too greedy.

705
00:40:32,261 --> 00:40:33,200
Where are you going?

706
00:40:34,080 --> 00:40:34,960
The hotel.

707
00:40:50,396 --> 00:40:51,652
Gui, I've confirmed it.

708
00:40:51,693 --> 00:40:53,531
Xia Guang Yuan will attend
the event as scheduled.

709
00:40:53,572 --> 00:40:54,440
Good.

710
00:40:55,270 --> 00:40:58,928
What about the deal
with Xiong the day after?

711
00:40:58,969 --> 00:41:00,880
I'll go personally. Leave it to me, Gui.

712
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:07,026
Finally, I'm going to meet Xia Guang Yuan.

713
00:41:20,282 --> 00:41:21,369
Are you home?

714
00:41:21,410 --> 00:41:22,320
I am.

715
00:41:22,393 --> 00:41:23,240
What's the matter?

716
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:25,040
Draw the curtains.

717
00:41:29,684 --> 00:41:30,920
Open the window too.

718
00:41:41,098 --> 00:41:42,160
Do you see me?

719
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:44,520
I do.

720
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:49,520
What are you doing up there?

721
00:41:49,969 --> 00:41:50,925
I am watching you.

722
00:41:53,576 --> 00:41:54,640
It's windy.

723
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,276
It's nothing.

724
00:41:58,440 --> 00:41:59,396
Do you have any plans two days later?

725
00:42:00,713 --> 00:42:02,040
I have work to do that day.

726
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:04,826
Are you going to cover the medical forum?

727
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,586
How did you know that?

728
00:42:07,076 --> 00:42:10,280
I always have a way of finding out about
the people and things that interest me.

729
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,400
I would like to ask you
for a favour, Mi Gu.

730
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:17,920
Go on.

731
00:42:39,580 --> 00:42:41,000
The test results are out.

732
00:42:41,392 --> 00:42:42,784
How is it? Is it poisonous?

733
00:42:43,494 --> 00:42:45,112
I can't exactly say it's poisonous,

734
00:42:45,153 --> 00:42:47,095
but it's not completely safe either.

735
00:42:47,315 --> 00:42:48,240
What do you mean?

736
00:42:49,720 --> 00:42:51,240
Do you know about its characteristics?

737
00:42:52,230 --> 00:42:54,105
It dissolves very easily in water.

738
00:42:55,506 --> 00:42:56,447
That's right.

739
00:42:56,488 --> 00:42:58,587
The inside of the pill is porous,

740
00:42:58,628 --> 00:43:00,218
it dissolve easily in water,

741
00:43:00,259 --> 00:43:01,880
making it easy for
the patient to swallow.

742
00:43:01,921 --> 00:43:03,640
This is the key feature
of 3D-printed drug.

743
00:43:04,735 --> 00:43:06,854
3D-printed drug? Are you sure?

744
00:43:06,895 --> 00:43:08,105
It can't be wrong.

745
00:43:08,153 --> 00:43:10,573
Our department is also
working on developing this.

746
00:43:11,439 --> 00:43:13,880
The main ingredient of the drug
is a combination of several herbs...

747
00:43:13,921 --> 00:43:15,870
that have a calming and sedative effect,

748
00:43:15,911 --> 00:43:18,051
synthesized by 3D printing technology.

749
00:43:18,591 --> 00:43:19,647
Most importantly,

750
00:43:20,343 --> 00:43:24,280
it is overdosed with an adjuvant
called aristolochia debilis.

751
00:43:24,767 --> 00:43:28,276
Long-term use of this drug
comes with the risk of liver cancer.

752
00:43:29,664 --> 00:43:31,040
What are you going to do with this drug?

753
00:43:31,690 --> 00:43:34,080
For an assassination mission?

754
00:43:35,320 --> 00:43:36,236
Put the drug away.

755
00:43:37,066 --> 00:43:38,200
I'll come and get it from you.
